|         1 |                     1 | update /*+parallel(2)*/ t1 set c = c+? where a = ? and b = ? | update /*+parallel(2)*/ t1 set c = c+5 where a = 1 and b = 5;update /*+parallel(2)*/ t1 set c = c+6 where a = 2 and b = 6;update /*+parallel(2)*/ t1 set c = c+7 where a = 3 and b = 7; |
|         3 |                     1 | update t1 set b = ? where a = ? and b = ?                    | update t1 set b = 2 where a = 1 and b = 1;update t1 set b = 1 where a = 2 and b = 2;                                                                                                    |
|         8 |                     0 | update t1 set b = ? where a = ? and b = ?;                   | update t1 set b = 2 where a = 1 and b = 1;                                                                                                                                              |
+-----------+-----------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
